<div class="container pb-5">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h1><%= @job.title %></h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="myTab" role="tablist">
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link active" id="home-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#home" role="tab" aria-controls="home" aria-selected="true">Details</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" id="profile-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#profile" role="tab" aria-controls="profile" aria-selected="false">Listing Owner Profile</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" id="messages-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#messages" role="tab" aria-controls="messages" aria-selected="false">Roles</a>
        </li>
<!--         <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" id="settings-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#settings" role="tab" aria-controls="settings" aria-selected="false">Apply</a>
        </li> -->
      </ul>

      <div class="tab-content">
        <div class="tab-pane active" id="home" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="home-tab">
          <h3 class="mt-3">Production Description</h3>
          <p>
            Seeking VO talent to discuss mindful eating for a well known mindfullness brand. In search of a VO artist who is calming and inviting. Easy to listen to. Non-judgmental. Some accents welcome as long as they are easy to understand and pleasant to listen to. Please no British/Australian/Canadian/European accents. American accent with a “hint’ of local dialects are ok.
          </p>

        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane" id="profile" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="profile-tab">
          ...owner information
        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane" id="messages" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="messages-tab">
          <h3 class="mt-3">Roles</h3>
          <div class="accordion mt-3" id="accordionExample">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                <h5 class="mb-0 d-flex justify-content-between">
                  <button class="btn btn-link" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                    <strong>Brandon (Lead):</strong> All Genders, 21+
                  </button>
                  <%= link_to "Apply", root_path, class: "btn btn-primary ml-auto" %>
                </h5>
              </div>

              <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>
                    Brandon – 18-36 years of age, Female who ideally goes by (He/Him) or a guy or gay guy. Any Race, Brandon is born female and transforms himself by getting a masculine haircut and starts dating Heather without letting her know that he was born a girl.(Lead Role)
                  </p>
                  <p>Ethnicity: All Ethnicities</p>
                  <p>Required Media: Headshot/Photo</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                <h5 class="mb-0 d-flex justify-content-between">
                  <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                    <strong>Heather (Supporting):</strong> Female, 21+
                  </button>
                  <%= link_to "Apply", root_path, class: "btn btn-primary ml-auto" %>
                </h5>
              </div>
              <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="card-body">
                 <p>
                   Heather – 18-36 years of age, Female who goes by (She/Her). Any Race, Heather starts dating Brandon under the assumption that Brandon is a natural boy. (Supporting Role)
                 </p>
                 <p>Ethnicity: All Ethnicities</p>
                 <p>Required Media: Headshot/Photo</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                <h5 class="mb-0 d-flex justify-content-between">
                  <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                    <strong>Female (Lead):</strong> Female, 18-50
                  </button>
                  <%= link_to "Apply", root_path, class: "btn btn-primary ml-auto" %>
                </h5>
              </div>
              <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>
                    pretty women, to model eyeglasses and sunglasses and discuss the process of on-line ordering. No prescription is necessary.
                  </p>
                  <p>Ethnicity: All Ethnicities</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- <div class="tab-pane" id="settings" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="settings-tab">...5123</div> -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
